      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some visible paint chips on the hood and a few minor scuffs along the door panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows signs of regular use and minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to ensure long-term reliability. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
