      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that balances performance with enduring value. This unit has been meticulously maintained to ensure mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic. A premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber pre-owned investment.",
      "price": 34800.0,
