    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it's honestly such a great find. It's in really solid condition and has been well-taken care of\u2014super dependable for whatever you need! Whether you're headed to work or hitting the road for a trip, it drives like a dream. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, delivering linear power and exceptional feedback. The double-VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced\u2014addressing the platform's primary technical concerns. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and chassis balance this M-car is known for. The exterior shows well with some honest age-appropriate patina, while the powertrain remains in peak operating condition for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular service records included. Clean title. Interior well-maintained. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience a perfect blend of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained sedan. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor signs of careful road use, while the interior remains a pristine sanctuary featuring supple, smoke-free upholstery and fully functional electronics. Under the hood, the engine hums with the confidence of regular professional servicing, including a recent comprehensive fluid flush and brake inspection. This car has been garaged its entire life and driven with respect, making it an ideal choice for someone who values a vehicle that looks and feels premium without the new-car price tag. Every button clicks as it should, and the ride quality is smooth and quiet. Ready for its next chapter with a driver who appreciates a well-documented and cared-for machine.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle offers a distinguished driving experience, blending mechanical integrity with timeless design. Each aspect of the automobile has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and comfort. A premier selection for the professional individual seeking a reliable, high-caliber transport solution.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years\u2014it still runs super smoothly and feels great on the highway! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next road trip or just your daily commute without any fuss, this is definitely the one. I'd love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded polyurethane bushings to mitigate common subframe fatigue. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving internal rotating assembly remains within factory tolerances. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering the raw, communicative steering and linear power delivery characteristic of this iconic M-platform.",
      "price": 32500.0,
